{{Quote|In fact, we' ve just entered phase three, with work commencing on the hypermatter reactor and the shield generators.|[[Orson Callan Krennic|Orson Krennic]], to [[Wilhuff Tarkin]]|<ref name="Catalyst">''[[Catalyst: A Rogue One Novel]]''</ref>}}
A '''hypermatter reactor''', also known as a '''hypermatter power plant''', '''hypermatter annihilator''' or '''hypermatter-annihilator reactor''', was a type of [[starship]] and [[battle station]] fusion [[reactor]] that generated power by destroying [[hypermatter]].<ref name="Awakens ICS">''[[Star Wars: The Force Awakens: Incredible Cross-Sections]]''</ref> The cores of such reactors were usually insulated with exfoliating [[doonium]] and [[dolovite]]. The hypermatter reactor of the [[DS-1 Orbital Battle Station|Death Star]] was an elaboration of the ones equipped on [[Star Destroyer]]s and other [[Galactic Empire|Imperial]] vessels.<ref name="Catalyst" /> A [[solar ionization reactor]] was a variant of the hypermatter annihilation reactor that used the destroyed hypermatter to create a miniature star inside the reactor chamber.<ref name="Complete Vehicles New">''[[Star Wars Complete Vehicles, New Edition]]''</ref>

